**4) How many and which conditions will participants be assigned to?**

All participants will be in the same condition and see the identical
materials. The only exception will be that each participant will see one
of three alternative vignettes as part of the sentencing measure
(intended to enhance generalizability)

**5) Specify exactly which analyses you will conduct to examine the main
question/hypothesis.**

We will use linear regression to rest the following hypotheses:

-   The focal DV is punitiveness will be positively related almost all
    of the listed measures

-   Most measures will be positively related to one another

